      <h3>Typhoon Tungsten Carbide Discs (3/8&Prime; Arbor Hole)</h3>
      <p>Max speed: 10,000 RPM. Use with Short Hub (A-69212). Unique structurally aligned tungsten carbide points that last long and do not load up quickly. Ideal for hard and soft woods, acrylic, die stone, plaster, hard rubber, and fiberglass. Use the fine grits for general shaping and sanding; the coarse grit is for rapid and aggressive shaping and roughing out work.</p>
