      <h3>Abrasive Wheels (3/8&Prime; Arbor Hole)</h3>
      <p>Max speed: 15,000 RPM. Use with Long Hub (A-69212L). For grinding, deburring, smoothing, and cleaning metals, stone, diestone, plastics, and other materials.</p>
