      <h3>Unitized Wheel (3/8&Prime; Arbor Hole)</h3>
      <p>A-10055: 2&Prime;, 1/4&Prime; thick. Max speed: 30,000 RPM. Use dry only, on edge. Made of non-woven fiber coated in aluminum oxide. For deburring, oxide and fire scale removal, cleaning, blending, and smoothing.</p>

      <h3>Felt Wheels (3/8&Prime; Arbor Hole)</h3>
      <p>Max speed: 20,000 RPM. Hard density, tightly compressed wool felt for polishing and lapping on metals, plastics, wood, and other materials. Use with polishing compounds.</p>
