      <h3>Optional Right Angle Adapter</h3>
      <p>A-69224: mounts on the Angle Grinder Attachment to convert it into a right angle handpiece. Fits into tight spaces for added versatility. Comes with 2 collets for 3/32&Prime; and 1/8&Prime; shank accessories. Can also use 1/16&Prime; and 3mm collets.</p>

